"{log_path}\n"
"\n"
"Tip: You can disable this prompt in Settings > YouTube."
msgstr ""
"Installa Homebrew (https://brew.sh) per consentire a BlindRSS di installarli "
"automaticamente, oppure installali manualmente con:\n"
"    brew install --cask vlc\n"
"    brew install ffmpeg yt-dlp\n"
"\n"
